<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,1122,1736]" pageId="2" pageNumber="530">Creamy white. Crown of head with submarginal brown stripe anteriorly. Face with arcuate lateral transverse stripes connected to median vertical stripe, brown; tiny spot on gena adjacent lorum, black.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,1122,1736]" pageId="2" pageNumber="530">Head shorter than median length of pronotum. Pronotum shorter than combined median length of scutum and scutellum.</paragraph>
